                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def3-849-18470301 t18470301-849-punishment-203"></join>Whipped, and discharged</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470301-name-1152" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-1152" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-1152" type="surname" value="GANS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-1152" type="given" value="AUSTIN EDWARD"></interp>AUSTIN EDWARD GANS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Thames police-constable No.</hi> 68.) I was on shore at Vauxhall, near the gas-works, on the 22nd of Feb., about half-past one o'clock in the afternoon—I saw the three prisoners go down a draw-dock close to the gas-works—they went directly to a coal-barge called the Glasgow, belonging to Mr. King—the property in it belonged to Mr. Spottiswood—I saw Mackey looking about him—he then jumped on the gunwale of the barge, took a large piece of coal, and put it by the side of the barge—he got up a second time, and took another large piece—he got up a third time, and then Lynch lifted Wright up, and they both took a piece, <hi rend="italic">chucked</hi> them out of the barge, and deposited them alongside of the barge—Mackey and Wright got up a second time, both together, and took another piece—they then each took a piece under their arms—I ran round the barge, and took Mackey—the other two were taken by another officer.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. HORRY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did you hear Mackey say he had met these boys, and been induced to go with them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470301-name-1153" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-1153" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-1153" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-1153" type="given" value="JOHN WILLIAM"></interp>JOHN WILLIAM TAYLOR</persName>
                  </hi>. I was with Gans, and assisted in taking the prisoners.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
